melting.patternModels.cricksPair

Class DecomposedInitiation

  • java.lang.Object
    • melting.patternModels.PatternComputation
      • melting.patternModels.cricksPair.CricksNNMethod
        • melting.patternModels.cricksPair.DecomposedInitiation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PatternComputationMethod
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AllawiSantalucia97, Tanaka04

    public abstract class DecomposedInitiation
extends CricksNNMethod
    This class represents one model to compute the initiation enthalpy and entropy. The duplex initiation is computed by the addition of an initiation penalty for the first base pair of the duplex and an initiation penalty for the last base pair of the duplex. It extends CricksNNMethod.
